359
00:49:17,500 --> 00:49:19,830
“塞班岛”

360
00:49:24,800 --> 00:49:26,630
0500时提高警觉
Heads up around 0500.

361
00:49:26,770 --> 00:49:30,260
补给品和弹药会送过去，完毕
You're going to have replacements and ammo coming up. Over.

362
00:49:31,640 --> 00:49:33,700
收到，请确认新口令
Roger. Make sure they have the new password.

363
00:49:33,850 --> 00:49:36,140
问“猎风”，答“战士”
Challenge: "Wind." Answer: "Talkers."

364
00:49:36,280 --> 00:49:38,110
一位纳瓦荷弟兄取的名字
That's what one of our Navajo brothers calls us.

365
00:49:38,250 --> 00:49:39,620
觉得怎么样？完毕
What do you think? Over.

366
00:49:40,720 --> 00:49:42,980
“猎风战士”我喜欢
"Windtalkers," I like it.

367
00:49:43,120 --> 00:49:46,490
好拉，老友，一夜平安，完毕
OK, Kemo Sabe, keep your butts down tonight. Over.

368
00:49:48,390 --> 00:49:50,920
这口粮真难吃
Biscuits? How can you ruin biscuits?

369
00:49:51,460 --> 00:49:54,830
你还真他妈爱抱怨
You are a whiny son of a bitch right now, aren't you?

370
00:49:57,100 --> 00:50:01,230
塞班晚上10点,东岸几点?
2200 hours in jungle hell - what does that make it on the East Coast?

371
00:50:01,610 --> 00:50:03,870
我怎么会知道
How the fucking hell should I know?

372
00:50:04,710 --> 00:50:06,640
7点…
Just seven...

373
00:50:07,980 --> 00:50:09,910
星期日早上8点
It's 8am, Sunday morning.

374
00:50:10,580 --> 00:50:13,420
希望我的床昨晚没被篡位
I hope my side of the bed didn't get taken up Saturday night.

375
00:50:13,620 --> 00:50:17,610
这么不放心她,迟早胃溃疡
Nell, you'll give yourself an ulcer, you keep worrying about her.

376
00:50:17,760 --> 00:50:19,850
这样我就可以回罗德岛了
Might get my ass sent back to Rhody, though.

377
00:50:19,990 --> 00:50:24,290
罗德岛辣妹不少哦
There's plenty of dollies outside of Rhode Island, Nell. Many plenty.

378
00:50:24,430 --> 00:50:27,590
-这里肯定没半个 -这还用说
- Well, there sure as shit ain't any here. - Ain't that the truth.

379
00:50:27,730 --> 00:50:32,800
她们全挤在德通海滩 世界上最美的女人
That's cos they're all in Daytona Beach. The most beautiful women in the world.

380
00:50:32,940 --> 00:50:35,670
战前有一次
This one time, before the war,

381
00:50:35,810 --> 00:50:42,710
我躺在沙滩上,有个美女… 叫茉莉,从水里上岸来
I'm lyin' on the beach and this sweet little thing named Molly comes out the water.

382
00:50:43,380 --> 00:50:46,680
走到我身边,问我饿不饿
She walks straight up to me and asks me if I'm hungry...

383
00:50:47,390 --> 00:50:49,720
因为她只吃条小热狗
cos she's havin' a weenie roast.

384
00:50:49,860 --> 00:50:51,690
哇靠!
Shit! Damn.

385
00:50:52,060 --> 00:50:54,220
于是我和茉莉…爽
Yeah, me and Molly, oh boy.

386
00:50:59,330 --> 00:51:02,630
现在却困在塞班岛上 身上背个巨无霸打火机
Now I'm on Saipan with this giant Zippo strapped to my back

387
00:51:02,770 --> 00:51:04,960
专门烤人肉
and I'm roastin' human beings.

388
00:51:10,980 --> 00:51:14,910
为什么会自愿从军 我实在搞不懂
Why I volunteered... beyond me.

389
00:51:17,050 --> 00:51:19,520
我倒是觉得蛮骄傲的
Damn, I'm proud to be here.

390
00:51:19,650 --> 00:51:22,020
我全家都是海军陆战队
My whole family's been in the Corps.

391
00:51:22,950 --> 00:51:24,950
老爸是终身职
My old man, he's a lifer.

392
00:51:25,320 --> 00:51:27,920
海上陆上都不可一世
An ass-kicker on the land and on the sea.

393
00:51:28,530 --> 00:51:30,430
在家一样作威作福
Around the house too.

394
00:51:35,030 --> 00:51:37,230
现在可能收敛点了
Maybe now he'll back off.

395
00:51:44,680 --> 00:51:46,610
帕帕斯
Pappas, I...

396
00:51:48,210 --> 00:51:50,270
希望你能帮个忙
I want you to do me a favor.

397
00:51:52,650 --> 00:51:54,810
万一我出了事
If anything should happen to me,

398
00:51:54,950 --> 00:51:57,680
这个请交给我太太
you make sure that my wife gets this.

399
00:52:00,330 --> 00:52:02,790
这是她亲手挑的
I mean, she picked them out and all.

400
00:52:03,260 --> 00:52:05,230
不要说这种话,奈尔
Don't talk like that, Nell.

401
00:52:06,600 --> 00:52:09,160
连玩笑都不要开
You don't even joke about shit like that.

402
00:52:09,840 --> 00:52:13,100
戴回去,你会平安回家
Now you put that ring back on. You're goin' home.

403
00:53:10,230 --> 00:53:12,460
喝过才谢我还不迟
Don't thank me till you've tried it.

404
00:53:13,000 --> 00:53:15,190
发信时你不在
You missed mailcall.

405
00:53:15,330 --> 00:53:18,390
“乔伊恩得斯收 丽塔史维登寄”

406
00:53:25,540 --> 00:53:27,640
他们在干嘛?
What the hell are they doin'?

407
00:53:28,510 --> 00:53:31,240
不知道,日落后就忙个不停
I don't know. They've been doin' it since sundown.

408
00:53:37,960 --> 00:53:40,190
听起来像是祈祷
Sounds like some kind of prayer.

409
00:53:47,630 --> 00:53:49,790
或许他们知道我们的命令
Maybe they know our orders.

410
00:54:04,620 --> 00:54:06,480
你下得了手吗,乔伊?
Think you could do it, Joe?

411
00:54:06,620 --> 00:54:08,640
不要一直想这问题,韩德森
Give it a rest, Henderson.

412
00:54:09,990 --> 00:54:12,480
不要想?我试过,可是…
Give it a rest? I keep tryin', but...

413
00:54:14,030 --> 00:54:16,050
该杀的是日本人,不是自己人
I'm here to kill Japs, not marines.

414
00:54:21,730 --> 00:54:24,170
你是个勇士，亚吉
I saw you a warrior, Yahzee...

415
00:54:25,200 --> 00:54:27,690
你是家族的荣耀
You will make your family proud.

416
00:55:17,120 --> 00:55:19,750
你在干嘛,老弟?
What the hell you think you're doin', boy?

417
00:55:19,860 --> 00:55:22,090
正要穿上制服
Getting on my uniform.

418
00:55:22,260 --> 00:55:25,860
知道你跟日本人 有什么差别吗?
You know the difference between you and a Jap, Yahzee?

419
00:55:28,700 --> 00:55:30,600
差在制服
It's that uniform.

420
00:55:31,270 --> 00:55:33,200
仅此而已
That's it.

421
00:55:34,810 --> 00:55:36,600
我了解你们这些人
See, I know you people.

422
00:55:37,080 --> 00:55:40,640
我清楚你们这些凤眼野蛮人
I know what kind of slanty-eyed savage you are, boy.

423
00:55:41,050 --> 00:55:43,710
落单时当心一点
You ought to be careful out here all alone.

424
00:55:44,520 --> 00:55:46,450
没有人照顾你时
No baby-sitter.

425
00:55:47,020 --> 00:55:48,950
我可能会把你看成日本鬼子
I might just take you for a Jap.

426
00:55:50,120 --> 00:55:52,390
你要让我穿衣服吗,奇克?
You gonna let me get dressed, Chick?

427
00:55:52,490 --> 00:55:55,620
还是继续演无知的白痴?
Or keep demonstrating what an ignorant fool you are?

428
00:56:00,700 --> 00:56:03,000
无知的白痴是吧?
How's that for an ignorant fool?

429
00:56:20,850 --> 00:56:22,840
拿啊,你试试看
Go ahead, try again.

430
00:56:34,500 --> 00:56:36,590
你不是想干什么吗?
You gonna do somethin'?

431
00:56:58,320 --> 00:56:59,790
奇克,住手
Chick! Come on!

432
00:56:59,890 --> 00:57:01,830
走开!
Get off me!

433
00:57:21,450 --> 00:57:23,970
-你没事吧,班? -没事
- You OK, Ben? - Yeah.

434
00:57:24,120 --> 00:57:26,380
班?恶心
Ben? Shit.

435
00:57:28,920 --> 00:57:33,620
我以为他是日本人 杀我弟兄,偷穿制服
I thought he was a Jap. You know, killed some marine for that uniform.

436
00:57:35,390 --> 00:57:37,260
再扯嘛,奇克
Sure you did, Chick.

437
00:57:37,700 --> 00:57:40,460
死红番不像日本鬼子吗?
Damn Injun looks just like a Jap, don't he?

438
00:57:40,600 --> 00:57:42,500
我不是死红番
Look, I'm no damn Injun.

439
00:57:43,230 --> 00:57:48,100
我是纳瓦荷人 母系是苦水族,父系是塔楼族
I'm Navajo, of the Bitter Water People, born for the Towering House clan.

440
00:57:51,840 --> 00:57:53,870
但长相蛮像日本人
But you do look like a Nip.

441
00:57:54,010 --> 00:57:58,920
下次要洗澡先通知我 否则我踢你屁股
Next time you decide to take a bath, Private, let me know, or I'll kick your ass.

442
00:58:02,850 --> 00:58:04,790
妈的败类
Fuckin' shitbird.

443
00:58:05,960 --> 00:58:08,590
他随时都需要人照顾
Supposed to be with a baby-sitter all the time, I thought.

444
00:58:08,760 --> 00:58:10,590
连出去打鱼时也一样
Out here huntin' salmon and shit.

445
00:58:12,930 --> 00:58:17,390
昨晚你看到的是 我们的庇护仪式
That ceremony you saw last night? It's called a protection ceremony.

446
00:58:18,370 --> 00:58:24,330
纳瓦荷人相信尸体未安葬前 灵魂会一直待在附近
Navajo believe, untila body's given a proper burial, the spirits stay near it.

447
00:58:24,840 --> 00:58:29,280
我们称恶灵为仙邸司
Chindis - that's what we call evilspirits. Demons.

448
00:58:32,050 --> 00:58:35,020
我从小不曾认真想过这问题
I haven't thought much about it since I was a kid.

449
00:58:35,150 --> 00:58:37,520
直到我目睹这些死尸
Till I saw those dead bodies.

450
00:58:37,660 --> 00:58:40,150
你是说你看得到鬼魂?
You telling me you saw ghosts, Private?

451
00:58:40,260 --> 00:58:42,620
不,我是说我不再害怕了
No, Sergeant. I'm telling you I won't freeze up again.

452
00:58:43,130 --> 00:58:46,100
因为你朋友在你额头上抹灰?
Because your buddy smeared ash on your forehead?

453
00:58:46,230 --> 00:58:50,460
没错,因为我朋友 在我额头上抹灰
That's right. Cos my buddy smeared ash on my forehead.

454
00:58:58,240 --> 00:59:00,300
你看过鬼吗?
You ever see ghosts?

455
00:59:05,220 --> 00:59:08,980
不要再问傻问题了 这是命令
No more stupid questions today, Private. That's an order.

456
00:59:40,650 --> 00:59:42,590
真好听
Sounds beautiful.

457
00:59:43,320 --> 00:59:45,290
无师自通吗?
You, uh, you self-taught?

458
00:59:46,120 --> 00:59:48,220
我爸爸常吹
My dad was always playing.

459
00:59:49,230 --> 00:59:52,360
他们不是说“拼不过他就…”
You know what they say: if you can't beat 'em...

460
00:59:52,500 --> 00:59:57,700
正确,这是我爸送我的
No shit. My dad, he... he gave me this thing.

461
00:59:59,000 --> 01:00:01,530
他以前叫我小猪魔笛
Used to call me the Pied Piper of the Pigs.

462
01:00:01,670 --> 01:00:05,510
我一吹它们就过来吃饲料
Used to bring 'em in for feeding with this little tune I played.

463
01:00:06,610 --> 01:00:09,710
我知道你不会停止吹笛子
I know I ain't gonna get you to quit playin' that thing, so...

464
01:00:09,850 --> 01:00:12,410
所以“拼不过他就…”
like you just said, if you can't beat 'em...

465
01:00:12,550 --> 01:00:14,780
我觉得声音不协调
I don't think it's gonna work.

466
01:00:16,290 --> 01:00:19,450
反正别无他法,管他的
Well, we ain't got much else to do out here. What the hell?

467
01:00:20,660 --> 01:00:22,290
好吧
OK.

468
01:00:23,060 --> 01:00:25,830
你起音,我来和
All right, you lead off. I'll follow you.

469
01:01:03,840 --> 01:01:05,890
第二侦查队0600出发
2nd Recon Company will move out at 0600

470
01:01:06,040 --> 01:01:07,560
沿四号路搜索下去
and scout along road 04.

471
01:01:07,710 --> 01:01:11,270
椰林西北边可能遭到轻微抵抗
You can expect light resistance northwest of the palm grove. Over.

472
01:01:12,280 --> 01:01:16,440
收到，何谓“轻微”？ 没有任何抵抗是轻微的，完毕
Roger. What do you mean, light? No resistance is light! Over.

473
01:01:17,480 --> 01:01:19,380
记住座右铭不问为什么
Remember, marine, "Ours is not to question why,

474
01:01:19,520 --> 01:01:20,610
只管拼命与牺牲
ours is but to do or die."

475
01:01:20,750 --> 01:01:22,340
“永远忠诚”完毕
Semper Fi. Over.

476
01:01:34,030 --> 01:01:37,000
亲爱的乔伊,你到底怎么了?
Dear Joe, how the hell are you?

477
01:01:38,040 --> 01:01:42,530
因为你不爱写信 就应该音讯全无吗?
Or, given that you're not much of a writer, should I not expect an answer?

478
01:01:42,670 --> 01:01:45,540
报上说,我军战果辉煌
The newspapers say our boys are doing great.

479
01:01:45,680 --> 01:01:50,110
但我想记者都没看到 肯尼欧湾医院的伤兵
But I don't think the reporters have been to Kaneohe Bay Hospital.

480
01:01:51,220 --> 01:01:54,280
前几天在瓦基基捡到只流浪狗
I found a stray dog the other day on Waikiki.

481
01:01:54,420 --> 01:01:57,080
带回家洗个澡留下来养
I gave him a bath and took him in.

482
01:01:57,220 --> 01:02:00,680
它令我想起你,但它比较可爱
He reminded me of you - but cuter.

483
01:02:02,590 --> 01:02:05,190
至少它晚上给我温暖
At least he keeps me warm at night.

484
01:02:06,430 --> 01:02:11,030
我尽量不想你 也不去想可能发生的事
I try not to think about you. About what might be happening over there.

485
01:02:11,870 --> 01:02:14,030
但是,有时候躺在床上
But sometimes, when I'm lying in bed,

486
01:02:14,170 --> 01:02:17,470
忍不住担心你的处境
I can't keep myself from wondering where you are.

487
01:02:17,610 --> 01:02:19,540
和过得好不好
How you're doing.

488
01:02:30,050 --> 01:02:32,020
你在干嘛?
What the hell you doin'?

489
01:02:32,690 --> 01:02:35,090
写信给我儿子
Writing a letter to my son.

490
01:02:35,230 --> 01:02:37,720
你忘了命令?不准流出一个字
Forget your orders? No letters out.

491
01:02:38,460 --> 01:02:41,590
上面不准邮件进入保育区
Command don't want postmarks going to the reservation.

492
01:02:46,370 --> 01:02:48,200
没听到吗?
Hey! You hear me?

493
01:02:53,880 --> 01:02:57,180
我回家后他就看得到啦
I thought that he might read 'em when I get home.

494
01:03:02,950 --> 01:03:04,980
他叫什么名字?
What's his name?

495
01:03:05,120 --> 01:03:06,990
你儿子
Your son.

496
01:03:07,430 --> 01:03:10,520
乔治,乔治华盛顿
It's George. George Washington.

497
01:03:12,000 --> 01:03:14,160
乔治华盛顿亚吉
George Washington Yahzee.

498
01:03:16,330 --> 01:03:18,460
听起来蛮响亮的
It's got a bit of a ring to it.

499
01:03:20,000 --> 01:03:21,900
我太太不太喜欢
My wife wasn't so sure.

500
01:03:22,440 --> 01:03:24,840
她比较传统
She's a little more traditional.

501
01:03:27,650 --> 01:03:30,110
-好漂亮的一家人 -给我看看,亚吉
- Nice-looking family. - Let's see, Yahz.

502
01:03:30,250 --> 01:03:34,840
乔治很有个性 他有自己的想法
Yeah, that George, he's quite a character. He's got a mind of his own.

503
01:03:38,420 --> 01:03:40,480
我可以抽一根吗?
Can I try one of those?

504
01:03:41,360 --> 01:03:44,190
-你抽烟? -抽着玩的
- You smoke? - Not really.

505
01:04:23,100 --> 01:04:25,500
-下来! -快下车!
- Dismount! - Get out of the truck!

506
01:04:26,670 --> 01:04:28,610
动作快!
Let's go! Let's go!

507
01:04:29,270 --> 01:04:31,170
-跟我来! -走!
- Follow me! - Let's go!

508
01:04:39,680 --> 01:04:41,550
我中弹了!
- I'm hit! - Yahzee!

509
01:04:43,650 --> 01:04:45,210
亚吉
Yahzee!

510
01:04:46,760 --> 01:04:48,250
我中弹了!
I'm hit!

511
01:04:48,430 --> 01:04:50,590
拿下来!好烫!
Take it off! It burns!

512
01:04:55,130 --> 01:04:57,570
你没中弹,闭嘴!
You're not hit. Just shut up. You're not hit.

513
01:05:15,590 --> 01:05:17,950
-散开! -动作快!
- Spread out! - Move!

514
01:05:26,860 --> 01:05:29,490
-炸弹从哪来的? -我们自己人
- Where the hell are they comin' from? - From us.

515
01:05:29,600 --> 01:05:32,770
-什么? -那不是日本人的炮
- What? - They're not Jap guns.

516
01:05:33,970 --> 01:05:37,370
-自己人炸自己人? -我们应该走四号路
- We're getting shot at by our own guys? - We're supposed to be on road 04.

517
01:05:37,510 --> 01:05:39,310
-通知团部 -没办法!
- Get the regiment on the horn. - I can't!

518
01:05:39,440 --> 01:05:43,780
-告诉他们炸到自己人 -不行!无线电炸坏了
- Tell 'em they're shelling... - I can't! The radio's out. It's been hit.

519
01:05:46,780 --> 01:05:49,550
-他们炸太近了 -日本鬼子一定在我们前面
- They're firing too short! - The Japs gotta be way ahead of us.

520
01:05:49,690 --> 01:05:51,210
想点办法
Do somethin'.

521
01:05:51,360 --> 01:05:53,760
跟我来
Shit... Follow me!

522
01:05:53,920 --> 01:05:56,590
-我们走错路了 -干!
- We're on the wrong fuckin' road! - Goddamn it!

523
01:06:18,720 --> 01:06:20,180
完蛋了!
God.

524
01:06:42,940 --> 01:06:44,570
龟孙子
Son of a bitch!

525
01:07:06,430 --> 01:07:08,420
不要怕,老哥!
I got you, mac!

526
01:07:13,440 --> 01:07:15,200
救护兵!
Corpsman!

527
01:07:15,940 --> 01:07:18,670
救护兵!
Corpsman!

528
01:07:24,150 --> 01:07:26,140
救护兵!
Corpsman!

529
01:07:27,790 --> 01:07:29,690
奈里!
Nellie!

530
01:07:33,520 --> 01:07:35,420
救护兵!
Corpsman!

531
01:08:04,890 --> 01:08:07,080
你说的没错,乔伊
You were right, Joe.

532
01:08:07,890 --> 01:08:09,590
我长得像日本人
I do look like a Nip.

533
01:08:09,730 --> 01:08:11,750
你在说什么?
What the hell are you talking about?

534
01:08:11,900 --> 01:08:13,260
穿上他们的制服
Putting on that Jap uniform.

535
01:08:13,400 --> 01:08:16,260
用他们的无线电 通知我方停火
Trying to get one of their radios, call off our guns.

536
01:08:16,400 --> 01:08:19,100
-笨主意 -闭嘴,让他说完
- That's stupid. - Shut up. Let him talk.

537
01:08:19,240 --> 01:08:22,300
-他不能出去 -这里不由你指挥,恩得斯
- He's not goin' out there. - You're not in charge here, Enders.

538
01:08:22,440 --> 01:08:24,930
我身负命令,枪头 我要保护他
I got orders, Gunny. He's my responsibility!

539
01:08:29,050 --> 01:08:32,350
他还年轻啊! 你们在杀自己人!
He's just a kid! You killed your own!

540
01:08:33,050 --> 01:08:37,680
你们有毛病啊! 你们在杀自己人!王八蛋!
What's wrong with you? You killed your own! Sons of bitches!

541
01:08:38,520 --> 01:08:40,750
你们在杀自己人!
You killed your own!

542
01:08:56,410 --> 01:09:00,140
-你确定要这么做? -马上就知道答案了,长官
- Sure you're up to this? - Find out soon enough, sir.

543
01:09:03,080 --> 01:09:06,210
-你想干嘛? -我跟他去
- What the hell are you doin' there? - I'm goin' with him.

544
01:09:06,350 --> 01:09:08,550
如果你没意见的话
If that's OK with you.

545
01:09:12,020 --> 01:09:13,920
枪给我
Give me the rifle.

546
01:09:17,290 --> 01:09:19,490
Horyo-da.

547
01:09:20,130 --> 01:09:22,190
“战俘”的日本话
It's Jap for prisoner.

548
01:09:22,970 --> 01:09:24,960
Horyo-da.

549
01:09:32,980 --> 01:09:34,970
Horyo-da.

550
01:09:37,980 --> 01:09:40,250
好啦,大家准备
All right, everybody be ready.

551
01:10:38,040 --> 01:10:39,130
Horyo-da!

552
01:10:45,680 --> 01:10:46,810
冲啊!
Now!

553
01:10:58,930 --> 01:11:00,690
打我
Hit me. Hit me.

554
01:11:16,610 --> 01:11:18,550
不要打我!
Please don't hit me!

555
01:11:58,290 --> 01:11:59,590
亚吉
Yahzee!

556
01:12:09,030 --> 01:12:11,160
杀了他!
Kill him!

557
01:12:16,710 --> 01:12:18,800
快点,杀了他!
Goddamn it, kill him!

558
01:12:25,480 --> 01:12:27,250
去无线电那!
Get on the radio!

559
01:12:35,730 --> 01:12:38,750
白鲍威,这是红卡森!
Bowie White, Bowie White, this is Carson Red!

560
01:12:41,400 --> 01:12:44,460
停火!你们在炸自己人!
Cease fire! Cease fire! You're shelling marines!

561
01:12:45,900 --> 01:12:47,840
中士!
Sergeant!

562
01:12:50,370 --> 01:12:52,400
停火!
Cease fire! Cease fire!

563
01:12:55,580 --> 01:12:57,670
距离加325米,立刻射击!
Add 325, fire for effect!

564
01:12:58,980 --> 01:13:02,610
调整!加325米,立刻射击!
Redirect fire. Add 325, fire for effect.

565
01:13:03,250 --> 01:13:05,220
走啦!
Let's go!

566
01:13:07,620 --> 01:13:09,650
摇高点!快!
Crank it up! Let's go!

567
01:13:09,830 --> 01:13:11,420
开火!
Commence fire!

568
01:13:11,600 --> 01:13:13,360
开火!
Fire!

569
01:13:20,900 --> 01:13:22,430
奏效了
Well, I'll be.

570
01:13:49,300 --> 01:13:51,100
请问什么事,上校?
Colonel. Can I help you, sir?

571
01:13:51,240 --> 01:13:54,970
我想找一位恩得斯中士 约瑟夫恩得斯
I'm looking for Sergeant Enders. Joseph F Enders.

572
01:13:56,170 --> 01:13:57,940
恩得斯
Enders.

573
01:14:06,550 --> 01:14:08,350
是的,长官
Yes, sir.

574
01:14:09,150 --> 01:14:12,350
据报你非常神勇
Report I read claims you went above and beyond.

575
01:14:13,990 --> 01:14:15,120
长官
Sir?

576
01:14:15,260 --> 01:14:17,590
我们已推荐你接受表扬
You've been recommended for commendation.

577
01:14:17,760 --> 01:14:20,960
我非常同意,但何必等待…
And I concur. But I don't see any point in you having to wait around

578
01:14:21,100 --> 01:14:25,360
繁复的公文往返
for all those formalities to work themselves out.

579
01:14:26,200 --> 01:14:28,570
我手边正好有个勋章
Not when I got one of these handy.

580
01:14:29,340 --> 01:14:31,740
恭喜,恩得斯
Congratulations, Enders.

581
01:14:31,880 --> 01:14:33,930
你救了不少同胞
You saved a lot of marines.

582
01:14:42,690 --> 01:14:47,350
这不是我一个人的功劳,长官 多亏了二等兵班亚吉的帮忙
I wasn't alone in that, sir. I couldn't have done it without Private Ben Yahzee.

583
01:14:47,460 --> 01:14:52,730
对,那位印地安人
Oh... Right. The, uh, Indian.

584
01:14:54,230 --> 01:14:57,760
抱歉,他是纳瓦荷人 母系苦水族
Begging the colonel's pardon, he's a Navajo, of the Bitter Water People,

585
01:14:57,940 --> 01:14:59,870
父系塔楼族
born for the Towering House clan.

586
01:15:00,670 --> 01:15:06,170
当然,纳瓦荷人,塔楼族
Of course. Navajo. Towering House clan.

587
01:15:12,720 --> 01:15:14,880
继续保持下去,恩得斯
You keep up the good work, Enders.

588
01:15:53,620 --> 01:15:55,890
把这个寄给奈里的太太
Send that to Nellie's wife.

589
01:16:36,430 --> 01:16:39,230
每次都有你的信,恩得斯
You ever not miss mailcall, Enders?

590
01:16:46,210 --> 01:16:48,770
我妈说,人家花时间写信
My mom says somebody takes the time to write a letter,

591
01:16:48,910 --> 01:16:51,070
你该花时间好好读
you should read the letter.

592
01:16:53,980 --> 01:16:56,420
你妈肯让你喝酒吗?
Does she let you drink, your mother?

593
01:16:57,090 --> 01:16:59,650
不肯,但她又不在这
No. But she's not here.

594
01:17:13,800 --> 01:17:17,500
-这是什么酒? -确定不是法国红酒
- What is it? - Well, it ain't Chianti, I'll tell you that.

595
01:17:17,640 --> 01:17:20,770
米酒类,是日本清酒 反正会醉就是了
It's rice wine. It's Jap sake. But it does the trick.

596
01:17:24,350 --> 01:17:26,910
你有多少这种东西?
How much of this crap do you have anyway?

597
01:17:29,750 --> 01:17:32,450
你这只耳朵有问题对不对?
You have a little trouble with that ear, don't you, Joe?

598
01:17:32,560 --> 01:17:37,760
问题在内耳,耳鼓耳膜之类的
Ah, real problem's the inner ear. It's anvils and stirrups and shit.

599
01:17:40,560 --> 01:17:42,660
我的平衡感不太好
I'm a little out of balance.

600
01:17:45,340 --> 01:17:48,360
你在山丘上表现很好,亚吉
You done good on that hill today, Yahzee.

601
01:17:48,570 --> 01:17:50,630
是啊,表现不错吧?
Yeah, I did, didn't I?

602
01:17:51,310 --> 01:17:53,970
一定了你一跳
I bet I surprised the shit out of you.

603
01:17:59,320 --> 01:18:01,650
你的情操很崇高,乔伊
It was a noble thing that you did, Joe.

604
01:18:02,350 --> 01:18:04,720
把银星勋章给奈里的太太
To give your Silver Star to Nellie's wife.

605
01:18:05,090 --> 01:18:07,220
我才不在乎奖章
I don't give a shit about medals.

606
01:18:17,500 --> 01:18:19,630
他们给我的第一枚
The first one they gave me...

607
01:18:21,300 --> 01:18:23,400
被我扔到海里去
I threw it into the ocean.

608
01:18:25,510 --> 01:18:27,980
那次是为了什么事?
What'd you get that one for?

609
01:18:28,110 --> 01:18:29,810
因为我撑着没死
For not dyin'.

610
01:18:31,620 --> 01:18:36,520
15个战友一起接受表扬 他们悉数阵亡
The 15 men who fought with me got decorated too. For dying.

611
01:18:37,250 --> 01:18:38,780
所以…
So...

612
01:18:43,690 --> 01:18:46,750
中尉前一晚就战死了
Lieutenant was killed the night before and...

613
01:18:48,630 --> 01:18:53,000
士官们也全死在登陆艇里
none of the sergeants even made it out of the landing craft, so...

614
01:18:55,510 --> 01:18:58,630
所以只好由我指挥 我第一次发号施令
that left me in charge. It was my first command.

615
01:19:00,880 --> 01:19:07,280
上面下令死守 某个鸟不拉屎的沼泽
Orders were to hold some shitty swamp marsh on the ass-end of nowhere.

616
01:19:10,890 --> 01:19:12,820
我只好听命行事
And I did.

617
01:19:16,230 --> 01:19:19,160
我手下的弟兄
All of the men under my command...

618
01:19:24,600 --> 01:19:26,540
信任我的人
men who trusted me...

619
01:19:31,710 --> 01:19:35,110
全都求我撤退
who begged me to pull back...

620
01:19:39,820 --> 01:19:41,750
结果没有一个生还
not one of them made it.

621
01:19:45,690 --> 01:19:48,620
除了一个固执的浑球
Just one stupid asshole.

622
01:19:54,500 --> 01:19:57,870
他们因此给我银星勋章
And for that, they gave me the Silver Star.

623
01:20:00,970 --> 01:20:03,060
他们叫什么名字?
What were their names?

624
01:20:04,370 --> 01:20:06,900
说他们的故事
It might be good to tell a story about 'em.

625
01:20:07,580 --> 01:20:10,310
最好也知道他们的名字和长相
You know, who they were and what they were like.

626
01:20:12,920 --> 01:20:18,050
纳瓦荷人鸟规矩真多 要干什么?
What a magical pile of Navajo horseshit. What the hell for?

627
01:20:18,720 --> 01:20:20,780
向他们致敬
To honor them.

628
01:20:21,660 --> 01:20:23,560
纪念他们
Their memory.

629
01:20:24,660 --> 01:20:29,330
那不是你的错,乔伊 你是听命行事
You know, it wasn't your fault, Joe. You were just followin' orders.

630
01:20:30,230 --> 01:20:31,960
是啊
Yeah.

631
01:20:32,100 --> 01:20:34,970
我是他妈的杰出陆战队
I'm a good fuckin' marine.

632
01:20:38,610 --> 01:20:40,970
所以派这个任务给我
That's why they gave me this detail.

633
01:20:45,650 --> 01:20:47,340
是喔
Yeah.

634
01:20:47,850 --> 01:20:50,120
我是他妈的杰出陆战队
I'm a good fuckin' marine.

635
01:21:19,950 --> 01:21:21,710
乔伊  怎么
- Joe! - What?

636
01:21:27,120 --> 01:21:29,390
你他妈的,乔伊恩得斯
Goddamn you, Joe Enders!

637
01:21:29,560 --> 01:21:30,960
没错
Really.

638
01:21:47,710 --> 01:21:49,650
不要想太多
It's all right.

639
01:21:50,750 --> 01:21:53,180
来,乔伊,我扶你
Come on, Joe. I got you.

640
01:23:13,600 --> 01:23:15,500
干什么?
What the fuck?

641
01:23:20,640 --> 01:23:24,070
我没醉死,亚吉,别乱整
I ain't that drunk, Yahzee. You cut that horseshit out.

642
01:23:53,400 --> 01:23:56,930
“塔那帕村第二侦查队”

643
01:23:58,380 --> 01:24:01,070
什么时候抵达村庄？
What's your expected arrival to the village? Over.

644
01:24:01,880 --> 01:24:03,640
大约1500，空军侦查报告
Around 1500. Aerial Reconnaissance reports

645
01:24:03,780 --> 01:24:05,300
没有活动，好像蛮安全的
no movement, looks secure.

646
01:24:05,450 --> 01:24:07,610
要求热食与信件，完毕
Request hot chow and mailif possible. Over.

647
01:24:09,320 --> 01:24:13,520
混合草莓与这瑞典玩意儿 就成了优酪乳
I'm gonna mix my daddy's strawberries in this Swedish concoction called yoghurt.

648
01:24:13,620 --> 01:24:16,250
所幸美国人会自创口味
God willin', America will develop the taste.

649
01:24:16,830 --> 01:24:21,390
战后你想干嘛,查理?
What about you, Charlie? What's life got in store for you after this mess?

650
01:24:22,100 --> 01:24:25,760
奇克拿来当女朋友的绵羊?
Sheep? As in Chick's girlfriend, sheep?

651
01:24:27,500 --> 01:24:31,370
查理家的羊群是四州最多的
Charlie's family owns the biggest flock in the Four Corners area.

652
01:24:31,510 --> 01:24:33,440
不是盖的?
No shit?

653
01:24:34,210 --> 01:24:37,510
-你是富翁嘛,白马 -还好啦
- You a rich man, Whitehorse? - We do OK.

654
01:24:37,650 --> 01:24:41,980
我要成立计程车队 那是我致富的秘诀
Taxis. A whole stinkin' fleet of 'em. That's how I'm making my millions.

655
01:24:43,120 --> 01:24:45,950
然后我要回到我的故乡
And then I'm goin' back to the motherland.

656
01:24:46,060 --> 01:24:49,080
在圣多里尼峭壁盖栋别墅
I'm gonna build myself a villa on the cliffs of Santorini.

657
01:24:49,260 --> 01:24:52,460
圣多里尼,哇,奢华
Ah, Santorini, my friends - that's living.

658
01:24:53,600 --> 01:24:56,760
不错,你呢,吉?
Sounds nice. What about you, Zee?

659
01:24:57,530 --> 01:24:59,370
我考虑去教书
Thinkin' about teaching.

660
01:24:59,500 --> 01:25:03,630
引进新知识到保育区
Ah, teaching. Bring a little something back to the reservation?

661
01:25:03,770 --> 01:25:08,730
事实上,是将保育区的知识 介绍给全世界
Actually, more interested in bringing some of the reservation back to the world.

662
01:25:08,880 --> 01:25:11,540
希望能到大学教美国历史
Hoping to teach college. American history.

663
01:25:11,680 --> 01:25:13,550
很符合我们的需要
Oh, that's just what we need.

664
01:25:13,680 --> 01:25:18,480
亚吉告诉大学生 卡司特怎么在小彼弘被剥头皮
Yahzee teachin' college boys about Custer's scalpin' at Little Bighorn.

665
01:25:19,220 --> 01:25:23,020
奇特卡森逼纳瓦荷人 迁徙三千哩又怎么说?
And what about Kit Carson, and what they did to the Navajo in the Long Walk?

666
01:25:23,190 --> 01:25:25,590
没读过吧,奇克?
You ever read about that, Chick?

667
01:25:26,330 --> 01:25:28,230
一定没有
Didn't think so.

668
01:25:29,730 --> 01:25:31,630
你呢,乔伊?
How about you, Joe?

669
01:25:32,640 --> 01:25:35,330
-什么? -战后你想干嘛?
- What? - What are you doin' after this mess?

670
01:25:35,470 --> 01:25:37,410
战争总是会结束的
It's gotta end sometime.

671
01:25:41,140 --> 01:25:44,310
亲爱的乔伊,今天有个好消息
Dear Joe, we got great news today.

672
01:25:45,010 --> 01:25:49,080
罗斯福总统宣布取消 夏威夷的灯火管制
President Roosevelt announced the end of blackouts on Hawaii.

673
01:25:49,220 --> 01:25:51,780
本以为遥遥无期
We thought the day would never come.

674
01:25:52,820 --> 01:25:56,950
10点仍有宵禁但影响不到我
There's still a ten o'clock curfew, but it doesn't matter to me.

675
01:25:57,690 --> 01:26:02,360
值班12小时后 累得只有精力写信
After a 12-hour shift I'm too tired to do anything but write letters.

676
01:26:05,130 --> 01:26:10,230
真正感觉到战况不错 战争随时都有可能结束了
There is a real sense that the war is going well, and could be over soon.

677
01:26:12,740 --> 01:26:17,240
越来越想你 你到底是死是活呢?
I think about you more and more. If you're alive or dead out there.

678
01:26:18,580 --> 01:26:22,710
我每天查信 心想迟早会有答案
I check the mailevery day, knowing there's going to be an answer.

679
01:26:22,850 --> 01:26:25,180
你有收到我的信吗,乔伊?
Are you reading these, Joe?

680
01:26:25,720 --> 01:26:27,660
听到我的话吗?
Are you listening?

681
01:26:33,060 --> 01:26:35,760
-左翼没有危险 -这区没有危险
- We're secure on the left side. - Area's secured.

682
01:26:35,900 --> 01:26:38,030
做好防御工事
Set up defense positions.

683
01:26:38,170 --> 01:26:40,330
奇克,负责扎营
Chick, bed 'em down for the night.

684
01:26:40,470 --> 01:26:42,200
哈利
Harri.

685
01:27:37,730 --> 01:27:39,060
怎么回事？
What's wrong?

686
01:27:40,060 --> 01:27:41,550
好痛
I'm hurting.

687
01:27:47,840 --> 01:27:50,170
这里有些止痛药
Here's some pain reliever.

688
01:28:03,690 --> 01:28:05,920
别担心，你没事
Don't worry, you'll be fine.

689
01:28:11,590 --> 01:28:12,790
谢谢，大叔
Thank you, Uncle.

690
01:28:32,650 --> 01:28:35,410
听起来蛮有感觉的
That's startin' to sound like something.

691
01:29:23,870 --> 01:29:25,990
不晓得你是个艺术家
I didn't know you were an artist.

692
01:29:26,440 --> 01:29:28,230
随便涂鸦
Oh, it's stupid.

693
01:29:28,370 --> 01:29:33,670
小时候常在祖母厨房桌上画
It's just something I would do as a kid on my grandmother's kitchen table.

694
01:29:34,210 --> 01:29:36,110
很不错
Well, it's nice.

695
01:29:36,250 --> 01:29:38,180
你信天主教?
You Catholic?

696
01:29:40,750 --> 01:29:42,680
以前啦
I used to be.

697
01:29:44,250 --> 01:29:47,310
正好想起受坚信礼的事
I was thinkin' about when they confirmed me.

698
01:29:47,460 --> 01:29:50,820
八岁那年,他们帮我抹圣水
I was eight, and they anointed me with the holy water.

699
01:29:50,960 --> 01:29:53,050
我还记得
And I remember...

700
01:29:55,300 --> 01:29:57,820
他们说我是基督的战士
they told me I was a soldier of Christ.

701
01:30:01,670 --> 01:30:05,440
不晓得什么时候迷失了自己
I guess somewhere along the way I must have switched units.

702
01:30:07,740 --> 01:30:09,680
是油
It's oil.

703
01:30:11,680 --> 01:30:14,950
坚信礼不用水,是用油
They don't use holy water to confirm. They use oil.

704
01:30:15,920 --> 01:30:17,940
我家也信天主教
I was raised Catholic too.

705
01:30:18,620 --> 01:30:20,950
上保育区内的教会学校
Mission school on the reservation.

706
01:30:21,990 --> 01:30:26,190
神父作弥撒时 不喜欢我们说纳瓦荷语
It's funny. Fathers didn't like us talking Navajo at Mass.

707
01:30:27,760 --> 01:30:30,160
有个礼拜天我忘记了
Of course, one Sunday I forgot.

708
01:30:31,670 --> 01:30:35,690
被处罚绑在地下室的暖炉上
They punished me by tying me to the radiator in the basement.

709
01:30:35,840 --> 01:30:37,770
整整两天
For two days.

710
01:30:39,410 --> 01:30:41,070
记得我当时也是八岁
I think I was eight too.

711
01:30:42,040 --> 01:30:46,470
现在可以自由说纳瓦荷语了
Well, they're sure lettin' you talk Navajo now. Yeah.

712
01:30:53,390 --> 01:30:58,220
战争结束后 或许你该来看看纳瓦荷村
You know, when this is over, maybe you should come out to Navajo country.

713
01:30:59,200 --> 01:31:02,930
纪念碑河谷很美,很幽静
Monument Valley is a beautiful place. It's peaceful.

714
01:31:03,530 --> 01:31:06,830
可以尝试军队里没有的东西
You know, we could do some things that you don't do in the Corps.

715
01:31:06,970 --> 01:31:12,460
比如骑马,吃炸面包,打猎
Like ride horses, eat fry bread, do some hunting...

716
01:31:15,310 --> 01:31:17,250
骑马
Horses.

717
01:31:22,420 --> 01:31:25,850
再说啦 到亚历桑那有好长一段路
I don't know. It's a pretty long drive to Arizona.

718
01:31:25,990 --> 01:31:29,650
很值得,你可以看看我儿子
But it might be worth it. You know, you could meet my son.

719
01:31:30,330 --> 01:31:32,820
他也可以见见乔伊恩得斯
And he could meet Joe Enders,

720
01:31:33,760 --> 01:31:38,170
保护他瘦弱老爸的恩人
the guy who watched over Daddy's scrawny ass.

721
01:31:42,810 --> 01:31:45,210
你一定是个好父亲,班
You must be a very good father, Ben.

722
01:31:47,080 --> 01:31:51,070
班?你以前不曾这样叫我
Ben. You know, you've never called me that before.

723
01:31:53,080 --> 01:31:56,570
恩得斯是哪一国名字?
Enders. What kind of name is that anyway?

724
01:31:57,290 --> 01:32:02,720
意大利,原本叫恩卓菲尼 被艾利斯岛移民局简化了
It's Italian. Used to be Endrolfini before some asshole at Ellis Island got hold of it.

725
01:32:04,930 --> 01:32:08,160
上尉要发一封密码信到司令部
Captain needs to code a message back to command post.

726
01:32:08,300 --> 01:32:09,790
你就是那个印地安人?
You the Indian?

727
01:32:09,930 --> 01:32:12,160
是的,我是那个印地安人
Yeah, I'm the Indian.

728
01:32:12,300 --> 01:32:15,630
只要几分钟,马上送你回来
It's just a few minutes' drive. We'll get you back in no time.

729
01:32:41,360 --> 01:32:44,990
-我有话跟你说,枪头 -等我一下
- I need to speak with you, Gunny. - Yeah. Give me a second.

730
01:32:45,530 --> 01:32:49,370
今天寄来的,吃过腌鲱鱼吗?
Got this with the mailtoday. You ever had pickled herring?

731
01:32:51,740 --> 01:32:53,680
我想调职
I need out.

732
01:32:54,280 --> 01:32:56,770
你在说什么?
What the hell are you talkin' about?

733
01:32:56,910 --> 01:32:58,850
目前的职务
This detail.

734
01:32:59,320 --> 01:33:01,310
我的任务
My duty.

735
01:33:01,450 --> 01:33:03,380
我无法执行
I can't do it.

736
01:33:04,020 --> 01:33:06,180
我需要你,恩得斯
Well, I need you, Enders.

737
01:33:06,320 --> 01:33:08,980
你救过很多同胞的命
Yeah. You've been saving a lot of marines.

738
01:33:12,900 --> 01:33:17,630
我要向营部司令申诉 我要调职
I'm requesting mast with battalion commander. I want out.

739
01:33:19,140 --> 01:33:24,000
是吗?大家都是妈妈的儿子 谁不想调职
Oh, yeah? You and me and every other mother's son. We all want out.

740
01:33:24,840 --> 01:33:28,540
只要东条英机和希特勒不死
Well, as long as there's a Tojo and a Hitler out there

741
01:33:28,680 --> 01:33:31,700
我们就得继续战,懂吗?
we have to keep on fighting. Is that understood?

742
01:33:33,280 --> 01:33:36,410
-你误会了 -我听得一清二楚
- You're not hearing me. - I'm hearing you just fine.

743
01:33:37,320 --> 01:33:39,810
现在全世界都在打仗
Now, there's a war goin' on worldwide,

744
01:33:40,360 --> 01:33:43,720
没空理会你的需求和愿望
and it ain't bein' waged on your wants and wishes.

745
01:33:43,860 --> 01:33:46,450
好好去睡一觉,这是命令
Now you get some sack time. That's an order.

746
01:33:46,600 --> 01:33:48,790
去你的!我下不了手!
Goddamn it! I can't do it!

747
01:33:49,500 --> 01:33:51,730
我无法执行任务!
I can't perform my duty!

748
01:34:07,230 --> 01:34:09,260
嘿,小朋友
Hey there, sweetheart.

749
01:34:09,440 --> 01:34:11,430
嗨,没有关系
Hi. It's OK.

750
01:34:12,310 --> 01:34:15,240
不要哭,不会有事
You don't have to cry. You're gonna be all right.

751
01:34:17,910 --> 01:34:19,970
我送你一个礼物
Got a present for you.

752
01:34:22,480 --> 01:34:24,470
巧克力
This is chocolate.

753
01:34:26,320 --> 01:34:28,980
吃吃看,很好吃
You see, you eat it... and it's good.

754
01:34:33,860 --> 01:34:35,790
很好吃
It's good.

755
01:34:36,300 --> 01:34:38,420
要不要尝尝看?
You want some?

756
01:34:41,670 --> 01:34:43,600
下次记得先嚼一嚼
You'll have to chew it next time. Here.

757
01:34:55,280 --> 01:34:57,370
哈利根,走!
Harrigan, go!

758
01:35:08,030 --> 01:35:09,790
炸弹过来了!
Incoming!

759
01:35:18,610 --> 01:35:20,200
跑!
Run!

760
01:35:20,370 --> 01:35:21,770
走!快跑!
Go! Run!

761
01:35:21,940 --> 01:35:24,030
哈利根!叫她跑!
Harrigan! Make her run!

762
01:35:25,710 --> 01:35:27,650
快点!来这边!
Come on! To me!

763
01:35:45,430 --> 01:35:47,300
哈利根!
Harrigan!

764
01:36:54,170 --> 01:36:56,330
该走了!
Come on, keep moving!

765
01:37:20,230 --> 01:37:22,160
退回来!
Fall back!

766
01:38:25,120 --> 01:38:27,220
求救!求救!
Help! Help!

767
01:38:43,580 --> 01:38:45,540
不能让他们活捉我们
I can't let 'em take us.

768
01:38:48,650 --> 01:38:50,840
说什么呀?
What are you talking about?

769
01:39:42,340 --> 01:39:43,530
留他活口
Don't kill him.

770
01:39:43,770 --> 01:39:44,900
他很重要
He's important.

771
01:39:46,310 --> 01:39:48,210
我们需要拷问他
We need to interrogate him.

772
01:41:18,800 --> 01:41:20,730
恩得斯
Enders!

773
01:41:21,770 --> 01:41:23,960
我找不到公牛和白马
I can't find Ox or Whitehorse.

774
01:41:27,440 --> 01:41:29,310
你有看到他们吗?
Have you seen them?

775
01:41:30,710 --> 01:41:32,470
他在那里
He's over there.

776
01:41:36,080 --> 01:41:37,880
噢,天啊
Oh, shit...

777
01:41:57,170 --> 01:42:00,940
这里不是应该很安全吗? 怎么回事?
This was supposed to be a secured area! What happened?

778
01:42:04,440 --> 01:42:06,780
我杀了他
I killed him.

779
01:42:07,750 --> 01:42:09,810
你什么?
You... you what?

780
01:42:10,550 --> 01:42:15,490
我用手榴弹 丢过去把他炸个粉碎
I took my grenade and... and I threw it and I blew him up.

781
01:42:23,960 --> 01:42:26,230
你他妈的疯了!
What the hell is wrong with you?

782
01:42:28,500 --> 01:42:29,970
亚吉
Yahzee!

783
01:42:30,370 --> 01:42:33,370
亚吉,不要!
Yahzee! Yahzee, no!

784
01:42:33,470 --> 01:42:34,910
起来!
Get up!

785
01:42:39,950 --> 01:42:42,680
来呀,动手啊
Come on. You can do it.

786
01:42:42,820 --> 01:42:45,880
放过他
- Yahzee. - Let him go.

787
01:42:46,020 --> 01:42:47,780
亚吉,不要
Yahzee, no.

788
01:42:49,060 --> 01:42:51,820
为何不…动手啊!
Go on. Why can't... Come on. Do it.

789
01:42:51,960 --> 01:42:53,890
-动手啊! -不
- Do it! - No.

790
01:43:26,790 --> 01:43:31,460
我们听说白马的事了，亚吉 我们会表扬他的功绩
We heard about Whitehorse, Yahzee. We shall honor his name and his memory.

791
01:43:31,630 --> 01:43:33,570
再会，查理再会
Farewell, Charlie, farewell.

792
01:43:34,570 --> 01:43:37,870
是的，查理再会
Yes, Charlie, farewell.

793
01:43:51,220 --> 01:43:54,950
你知道,白马…救过我一命
You know, Whitehorse... he saved my bacon.

794
01:43:58,930 --> 01:44:02,620
不知道乔治卡斯特会怎么想
Wonder what George Armstrong Custer would make of that.

795
01:44:05,430 --> 01:44:10,660
记得祖父以前坐在廊下 讲猎印地安人的事
I remember my granddaddy sittin' on the porch talkin' about huntin' Indians,

796
01:44:10,800 --> 01:44:13,900
讲得简直像猎地鼠一般
like he was talkin' about gophers or somethin'.

797
01:44:15,310 --> 01:44:19,340
猎一个赚三块美金
About gettin' paid three dollars per Comanche ear.

798
01:44:21,410 --> 01:44:23,940
我知道很难想像
I know. Gets you thinkin'.

799
01:44:25,820 --> 01:44:31,220
再过50年,或许我们 跟日本人会变成朋友
Another 50 years, who knows, we could be sittin' down with the Nipponese.

800
01:44:31,360 --> 01:44:34,590
喝着清酒,随意哈拉
Drinkin' their sake, shootin' the shit...

801
01:44:36,860 --> 01:44:39,490
聊看看还可以打谁
lookin' for somebody else's ass to kick.

802
01:44:42,230 --> 01:44:44,130
你想太多了
You think too much.

803
01:44:49,340 --> 01:44:51,900
第一次有人这样称赞我
First time I ever been accused of that.

804
01:44:59,620 --> 01:45:02,990
“海陆第八营第二侦察连 塞班岛”

805
01:45:54,570 --> 01:45:58,300
告诉过你别一个人到处晃
Thought I told you not to go traipsing around on your own.

806
01:46:05,180 --> 01:46:10,520
你知道,查理祝福过我儿子 出生时,以纳瓦荷传统方式
You know, Charlie blessed my son in the Navajo way the day he was born.

807
01:46:17,600 --> 01:46:20,900
他曾怀疑老美会保护我们
He wondered about cowboys watching Indians' backs.

808
01:46:21,630 --> 01:46:24,000
老是感觉不对劲
Something about it didn't seem right.

809
01:46:24,770 --> 01:46:27,640
我觉得查理只是多心
I thought it was Charlie just being Charlie.

810
01:46:29,040 --> 01:46:34,140
他其实一点都不想来打仗 是我说服他的
He didn't even want to come to this damn war. I talked him into it.

811
01:46:38,350 --> 01:46:40,080
或许你错了
Maybe you made a mistake.

812
01:46:51,630 --> 01:46:53,830
大家可能都错了
Maybe we all did.

813
01:46:55,070 --> 01:46:56,930
我只是奉命行事,班
I was following orders, Ben.

814
01:46:58,270 --> 01:47:00,930
我奉命保护密码
My orders were to protect the code.

815
01:47:01,810 --> 01:47:07,370
如果你们其中一人被补 一旦密,密码就没用了
If one of you got caught, talked, the code would be useless.

816
01:47:14,950 --> 01:47:16,980
我只是奉命行事,班
I was following orders, Ben.

817
01:47:20,160 --> 01:47:24,620
当然是,乔伊 你是他妈的杰出军人
Course you were, Joe. You're a damn good fuckin' marine.

818
01:47:40,180 --> 01:47:42,200
海盗要找你
The Viking wants to see you.

819
01:47:43,220 --> 01:47:45,240
他说马上
He says right away.

820
01:47:52,530 --> 01:47:55,520
跟大伙说明一下怎么回事
I want you to brief everybody, make clear what's happenin'.

821
01:47:55,690 --> 01:47:58,360
我打头阵没问题,枪头
All right. Got no problem with point, Gunny.

822
01:47:58,430 --> 01:47:58,690
我打头阵没问题,枪头
All right. Got no problem with point, Gunny.

823
01:48:00,670 --> 01:48:01,860
Yeah.

824
01:48:02,000 --> 01:48:06,130
第八营已经出发了 我们要迎头赶上,领先他们
The 8th is moving out already and we need to be ahead of 'em.

825
01:48:06,240 --> 01:48:10,040
目标是那边那块巨石
The destination is that big piece of rock you see over there.

826
01:48:10,180 --> 01:48:13,510
这个岛的最后防御据点
The last defensible ridge on this island.

827
01:48:13,650 --> 01:48:18,280
攻下那山头 塞班几乎就是我们的了
Now, thinkin' is, we take the mount, Saipan is pretty much ours.

828
01:48:22,090 --> 01:48:26,150
昨天轰炸机 把山头炸得差不多了
Yesterday, bombers beat the shit out of that rock.

829
01:48:26,560 --> 01:48:30,790
上面很紧张,可能遭到顽抗
The brass is nervous. They expected more resistance over there.

830
01:48:31,800 --> 01:48:34,320
要我们过去查看一下
Now they want us to go over and check it out.

831
01:48:35,470 --> 01:48:37,990
他们要我们去哪里?
So where the hell they got us now?

832
01:48:38,140 --> 01:48:40,000
翻上山头
Goin' up the mountain.

833
01:48:40,470 --> 01:48:42,740
偷窥一下
Have ourselves a little peek.

834
01:48:44,940 --> 01:48:48,610
要密码战士打头阵是有原因的
That codetalker is out front for a reason.

835
01:48:49,150 --> 01:48:51,580
他正好派上用场
That's exactly where I need him to be.

836
01:48:52,790 --> 01:48:55,480
假如你俩之间有嫌隙
If there's still a problem between the two of you,

837
01:48:55,620 --> 01:48:59,220
最好现在立刻摆平
I would like to straighten that out, right here, right now.

838
01:49:01,330 --> 01:49:03,890
-我没事的,枪头 -好极了
- No problem here, Gunny. - That's good.

839
01:49:04,730 --> 01:49:06,820
但我还有一个问题
But there's still one here.

840
01:49:08,400 --> 01:49:11,060
你只须做你该做的事
You just do what you're supposed to do, Sergeant.

841
01:49:11,200 --> 01:49:13,230
不多也不少
Nothing more, nothing less.

842
01:49:19,510 --> 01:49:21,450
恩得斯
Enders.

843
01:49:22,650 --> 01:49:24,810
恩得斯,又一封你的信
You got another letter.

844
01:50:30,180 --> 01:50:32,010
不要动!
Freeze!

845
01:50:43,130 --> 01:50:46,960
要命!我们站在地雷区中央!
Jesus Christ! We're in the middle of a goddamn minefield!

846
01:50:47,100 --> 01:50:49,620
奇克会带我们脱离的,是吧?
Chick's gonna get us out. Right, Chick?

847
01:50:50,470 --> 01:50:52,400
当然
Sure I am.

848
01:50:54,110 --> 01:50:56,200
跟着奇克排一纵队
One line after Chick.

849
01:51:01,080 --> 01:51:03,010
帕帕斯
Pappas.

850
01:51:05,150 --> 01:51:06,950
帕帕斯
Pappas.

851
01:51:08,150 --> 01:51:10,090
走呀,希腊人
Move, Greek.

852
01:51:10,690 --> 01:51:13,350
我的蛋蛋会被炸个粉碎!
I'm gonna get my fuckin' balls blown off out here!

853
01:51:20,830 --> 01:51:22,770
亚吉,站住!
Yahzee! Stop!

854
01:51:44,860 --> 01:51:46,790
躲开!
Move out!

855
01:52:26,530 --> 01:52:27,970
亚吉
Yahzee!

856
01:52:46,220 --> 01:52:48,280
射得好,帕帕斯
Nice shootin', Pap.

857
01:53:07,610 --> 01:53:11,240
第八营进来了,查看另一边
The 8th's movin' in. We'd better check out the other side.

858
01:53:11,380 --> 01:53:13,400
了解,你还好吧?
Got it. You all right?

859
01:53:14,280 --> 01:53:18,050
奇克负责左翼,恩得斯到右翼 我们会用榴弹炮掩护你们
Chick, take the left flank. Enders, go right. We'll cover you with a 30.

860
01:53:18,180 --> 01:53:19,840
-就位 -好了吗?
- On it. - All right?

861
01:53:19,990 --> 01:53:22,080
好,走吧!
OK, let's go!

862
01:53:22,420 --> 01:53:23,350
出发!
Move!

863
01:53:44,410 --> 01:53:46,570
贺玛斯德!
Hjelmstad!

864
01:53:46,710 --> 01:53:48,980
-快帮他! -枪头!
- Help him up! - Gunny!

865
01:53:52,620 --> 01:53:54,550
快
Come on. Come on.

866
01:54:06,600 --> 01:54:09,330
-天啊 -乔伊!
- Christ. - Joe! Joe!

867
01:54:11,700 --> 01:54:13,400
撕开衣服
Tear him open.

868
01:54:14,410 --> 01:54:16,370
要来点吗啡吗?
You want morphine?

869
01:54:16,510 --> 01:54:18,170
-要来点吗啡吗? -好
- You want morphine? - Yeah.

870
01:54:22,480 --> 01:54:24,510
你不会有事的,长官
You'll be all right, sir.

871
01:54:28,150 --> 01:54:30,210
可恶!亚吉,过来!
Goddamn it, Yahzee, get over here!

872
01:54:31,160 --> 01:54:32,490
干!
Fuck!

873
01:54:33,430 --> 01:54:36,490
奇克,看着他
Chick... Stay with him.

874
01:54:39,060 --> 01:54:40,190
有我在
I got ya.

875
01:56:16,900 --> 01:56:18,990
我叫你照顾枪头
I told you to stay with Gunny.

876
01:56:19,630 --> 01:56:21,460
枪头挂了
Gunny's gone.

877
01:56:41,490 --> 01:56:44,480
我们出不去了,对不对?
We're not gonna make it out of here, are we, Joe?

878
01:56:46,090 --> 01:56:48,460
我快没弹药了,乔伊
I'm runnin' out of ammo here, Joe.

879
01:56:52,330 --> 01:56:54,770
我不想死在这S坑里
I don't wanna die in this shithole.

880
01:56:58,300 --> 01:57:00,400
你不会死的
You're not gonna die.

881
01:57:03,010 --> 01:57:04,870
不会有人死的
Nobody else is gonna die.

882
01:57:14,750 --> 01:57:19,190
我们会活着 我们会活着出去
We're gonna make it. We're gonna make it out of here.

883
01:57:19,260 --> 01:57:19,550
我们会活着 我们会活着出去
We're gonna make it. We're gonna make it out of here.

884
01:58:26,260 --> 01:58:30,490
第八营被困在空地 我们必须请求空中支援
8th's caught out in the open. We gotta call in the flyboys.

885
01:58:34,930 --> 01:58:37,460
我去拿那个无线电,掩护我
I'm gonna get that radio. Cover me.

886
01:59:07,030 --> 01:59:09,090
无线电被他拿走了,亚吉!
He got the radio, Yahzee!

887
01:59:40,430 --> 01:59:42,300
掩护我,我去了!
Cover me! I'm going!

888
01:59:45,800 --> 01:59:47,970
退回去!
Stay back!

889
02:00:01,250 --> 02:00:02,780
王八蛋!
Fuckers!

890
02:00:53,810 --> 02:00:56,210
救不回你朋友的
It won't bring your friends back.

891
02:00:59,310 --> 02:01:01,470
你懂什么叫朋友?
What do you know about friends?

892
02:01:42,220 --> 02:01:44,420
快呼叫空中支援
Get us some air support!

893
02:01:58,440 --> 02:02:01,500
白鲍威,红卡森呼叫 亚历桑那
Bowie White, this is Carson Red, Arizona.

894
