重复,红卡森呼叫,亚历桑那
I say again, Carson Red, Arizona.

895
02:02:10,720 --> 02:02:12,480
指示座标!
Coordinates!

896
02:02:12,620 --> 02:02:16,490
2-20,麦克,36
Two-twenty, Mike, three-six.

897
02:02:27,630 --> 02:02:27,860
好,走吧
All right, let's go.

898
02:02:31,140 --> 02:02:33,400
我们要杀出重围
We're gonna make it outta here.

899
02:03:08,670 --> 02:03:10,570
可恶,乔伊
Damn it, Joe.

900
02:03:13,650 --> 02:03:15,580
快点动手
Just get it over with.

901
02:03:16,680 --> 02:03:18,620
闭嘴,班
Shut up, Ben.

902
02:03:38,240 --> 02:03:40,140
动手,乔伊
Do it, Joe.

903
02:03:41,570 --> 02:03:43,470
动手啊!
Do it!

904
02:03:46,310 --> 02:03:48,510
不能再死人了,班
No one else is gonna die, Ben.

905
02:03:52,520 --> 02:03:54,250
不会再有人送命了
No one else is dying.

906
02:05:21,810 --> 02:05:23,710
乔伊,我们成功了
Joe, we did it.

907
02:05:25,380 --> 02:05:27,140
老天…
God...

908
02:05:28,110 --> 02:05:29,740
老天
God!

909
02:05:30,450 --> 02:05:33,280
Oh, God... Oh, Joe...

910
02:05:48,530 --> 02:05:51,090
我们今天救了不少海陆弟兄
We saved a lot of marines today.

911
02:05:55,110 --> 02:05:57,100
是啊,班
Yeah, we did, Ben.

912
02:06:03,480 --> 02:06:05,310
查理…
Charlie...

913
02:06:05,720 --> 02:06:08,050
你知道我不想杀他的
You know I didn't want to.

914
02:06:11,160 --> 02:06:12,880
对吧?
Right?

915
02:06:24,170 --> 02:06:26,360
圣母玛丽亚
Hail... HailMary...

916
02:06:26,500 --> 02:06:28,060
万福
full of grace...

917
02:06:28,240 --> 02:06:29,540
our...

918
02:06:30,280 --> 02:06:32,510
天主与你同在
our Lord is with thee...

919
02:06:41,320 --> 02:06:44,410
圣母玛丽亚,上帝之母
Holy Mary, mother of God...

920
02:06:46,020 --> 02:06:47,960
保佑我们
pray for us...

921
02:06:56,600 --> 02:06:58,900
我干掉最后一个了,乔伊
I got the last of 'em, Joe.

922
02:08:26,960 --> 02:08:29,150
他名叫乔伊恩得斯
His name was Joe Enders...

923
02:08:29,860 --> 02:08:32,090
南费城人
from South Philadelphia.

924
02:08:32,930 --> 02:08:34,990
他是个英勇的战士
He was a fierce warrior.

925
02:08:36,870 --> 02:08:38,770
是优秀海军陆战队
A good marine.

926
02:08:48,680 --> 02:08:51,980
如果你要说他的故事,乔治
If you ever tell a story about him, George...

927
02:08:53,620 --> 02:08:55,780
就说他是我的朋友
say he was my friend.

928
